  &lt;li&gt;Take note and relay customer feedback and insights to Aircall&#39;s internal teams such as the tech, marketing and product teams, in order to constantly improve the customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Maintain an expert-level knowledge of our products and internal management systems as well as curiosity and awareness of new initiatives within in the industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What we are looking for:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
